9-04-12T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5a598575b2f6ed45d6c17721010667d33d26d7","tid":1099933,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"<em>《清史稿》<br />\n未幾，靖南王耿繼茂、總督李率泰等攻克廈門，敵驚潰，<span style=\"color: red;\">瑯募荷蘭國水兵</span>，以夾板船要擊，斬級千餘，乘勝取浯嶼、金門二島。</em><br />\n譯：勾結外國勢力，屈勁外援可恥<br />\n<br />\n<em><br />\n論曰：台灣平，瑯專其功。然啟聖、興祚經營規畫，戡定諸郡縣。及金、廈既下，<span style=\"color: red;\">鄭氏僅有台澎，遂聚而殲。先事之勞，何可泯也？</span></em><br />\n譯：等餵王除左識tap in執雞仲識啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n<em>及瑯出師，啟聖、興祚欲與同進，瑯遽疏言未奉督撫同進之命。上命啟聖同瑯進取，止興祚毋行。既克，<span style=\"color: red;\">啟聖告捷疏後瑯至，賞不及，鬱鬱發病卒。</span>功名之際，有難言之矣。</em><br />\n譯：搶人功勞，逼害隊友<br />\n<br />\n<em>大敵在前，將帥內相競，審擇堅任，一戰而克。非聖祖善馭群材，曷能有此哉？</em><br />\n譯：冇康熙carry你有今日？"},{"pid":"2f82681bb1ce1f50135bdf916dc6fd1a697541c1","tid":1099933,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c12a9f0e24fcd9a303489496c3ae73ccc6195ada","tid":1099933,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ade147006342efa70d7ed921c7444072ea9578d5","tid":1099933,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47092ebe738dbd90f75378a17765a9c5f43fddf7","tid":1099933,"uid":7439,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:41:09.000Z","msg":"<em>《清實錄康熙朝實錄》<br />\n上曰、施琅何如。席柱奏曰、施琅人材頗優。善於用兵。但行事微覺好勝。上曰。<span style=\"color: red;\">粗魯武夫、未嘗學問。度量褊淺、恃功驕縱</span>、此理勢之必然也</em><br />\n<br />\n康熙：施琅你管理到咁點x得！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db8f302acf9e2a0ac97af53b61faa33acb40870","tid":1099933,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"728f9e7841ad140bd156f8477b3ecf4ecf9927fc","tid":1099933,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:03:35.000Z","msg":"福建晉江,姓施<br />\n出過一個大將軍叫施琅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:01:08.000Z","msg":"俾韋小寶當狗撚"},{"pid":"9c41f23d01c41163e0e72e7ced1df6d01c8eb747","tid":1099933,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadfb4fc640e8bc5af7c1d4cd11b4aff8253073d","tid":1099933,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ade147006342efa70d7ed921c7444072ea9578d5","tid":1099933,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47092ebe738dbd90f75378a17765a9c5f43fddf7","tid":1099933,"uid":7439,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:41:09.000Z","msg":"<em>《清實錄康熙朝實錄》<br />\n上曰、施琅何如。席柱奏曰、施琅人材頗優。善於用兵。但行事微覺好勝。上曰。<span style=\"color: red;\">粗魯武夫、未嘗學問。度量褊淺、恃功驕縱</span>、此理勢之必然也</em><br />\n<br />\n康熙：施琅你管理到咁點x得！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}